---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="APV - Association Philatelique de Valence">

  <section class="px-6 pt-10 md:pt-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto overflow-hidden stamp-card postal-frame">
      <img
        src="/hero-accueil.jpg"
        alt="Philatelie - Association Philatelique de Valence"
        class="w-full h-auto max-h-[420px] object-cover object-center"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 pt-12 pb-16 md:pt-16 md:pb-20 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="page-subtitle tracking-[0.28em] mb-6">Centenaire 1926 — 2026 · L&rsquo;APV f&ecirc;te ses 100 ans</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-[2.4rem] sm:text-[3.2rem] md:text-[3.8rem] font-semibold text-stone-900 leading-[1.1] mb-6">
        Association<br />Philat&eacute;lique de Valence
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-stone-600 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Une association amicale de passionn&eacute;s de timbres,<br class="hidden sm:block" />
        d&rsquo;histoire postale et de moments partag&eacute;s.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[14px] text-stone-500 max-w-md mx-auto mb-11 leading-relaxed">
        Ici, on &eacute;change, on apprend, on d&eacute;couvre — d&eacute;butants comme confirm&eacute;s.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
        <a href={`${base}adhesion`} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-stone-400 bg-[#faf7f2] text-stone-800 px-9 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-[13px] font-medium hover:bg-white transition">Nous rejoindre</a>
        <a href={`${base}agenda`} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-stone-300 bg-white text-stone-700 px-9 py-3.5 rounded-lg text-[13px] font-medium hover:bg-stone-50 transition">Prochains rendez-vous</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <a href="https://www.ledauphine.com/culture-loisirs/2026/06/17/ce-n-est-pas-qu-un-truc-de-vieux-l-association-philatelique-a-100-ans" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block text-center perforated bg-white/80 py-8 px-6 hover:shadow-sm transition">
        <p class="font-serif text-[1.2rem] md:text-[1.35rem] text-stone-800 leading-relaxed italic mb-3">&laquo;&nbsp;Ce n&rsquo;est pas qu&rsquo;un truc de vieux.&nbsp;&raquo;</p>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-stone-400 tracking-wide uppercase">Le Dauphin&eacute; Lib&eacute;r&eacute; — &agrave; propos de l&rsquo;APV</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto stamp-card postal-frame paper p-10 md:p-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] text-accent-600 uppercase mb-4">&Eacute;v&eacute;nement 2026</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-[1.85rem] md:text-[2.15rem] font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Expophil Rh&ocirc;ne-Alpes</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 mb-1">Congr&egrave;s r&eacute;gional et centenaire de l&rsquo;APV</p>
      <p class="text-stone-500 text-[14px] mb-8">Samedi 20 et dimanche 21 juin 2026<br />Maison de la Vie Associative - Valence</p>
      <a href={`${base}actualites/expophil-2026`} class="inline-flex text-[13px] font-medium text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-900 transition">D&eacute;couvrir l&rsquo;&eacute;v&eacute;nement</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-6 py-20 border-t border-stone-200/60">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 md:gap-20">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-6">Pourquoi nous rejoindre ?</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[15px] text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Depuis un si&egrave;cle, l&rsquo;APV r&eacute;unit des amateurs de timbres, d&rsquo;histoire postale, de marcophilie et de cartophilie.</p>
          <p>On y &eacute;change sans chichi, on montre ses collections, on se conseille. L&rsquo;ambiance est simple, humaine, fid&egrave;le &agrave; l&rsquo;esprit des clubs de passionn&eacute;s.</p>
          <p>Chaque ann&eacute;e, l&rsquo;association organise la F&ecirc;te du Timbre avec La Poste et participe &agrave; la vie philat&eacute;lique de la r&eacute;gion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-6">Nous rencontrer</h2>
        <div class="stamp-card postal-frame paper p-7 space-y-5 text-[15px]">
          <div>
            <p class="label">R&eacute;unions</p>
            <p class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Tous les jeudis apr&egrave;s-midi</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="label">Lieu</p>
            <p class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Maison de la Vie Associative</p>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-[14px]">74 route de Mont&eacute;lier, 26000 Valence</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="label">Contact</p>
            <a href="mailto:contact@assophil-valence.net" class="text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-900 transition font-medium whitespace-nowrap">contact@assophil-valence.net</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>